p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  ' Congratulations on winning a Queen's Award in
  => @form_answer.award_type_short_name
  => "#{@form_answer.award_year.year}"
  = "[#{@form_answer.urn}]"

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  = "Dear #{@name},"

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  ' I am delighted to inform you that Her Majesty The Queen has been graciously pleased to approve the Prime Minister's recommendation that your organisation should receive a Queen's Award for Enterprise in
  => @form_answer.award_type_full_name
  ' this year. We have also informed the Head of your organisation by email.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  ' If you are a Collaborator please liaise with the account holder.

p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  ' Please read this email carefully as it contains important information about actions you need to do now.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  ' The Award will be conferred on
  = @deadline.try :strftime, "%A %d %B %Y"
  ' , Her Majesty's birthday. Although you can make arrangements for publicity now,
  span style="font-weight: 700;"
    ' there is a strict embargo preventing public announcement or publication of any Awards information until
    = @deadline.try :strftime, "%H.%M hrs on %d %B %Y"
    ' . You must not make any announcement about your Award, either to employees or outside your organisation, before this date.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  ' Under the terms of the embargo we will provide information to the media of the winners at
  =< @media_deadline
  ' , and the list of winners will be published in the Supplement to the London Gazette on
  = @deadline.try :strftime, "%d %B %Y"
  ' .

p style="font-weight: 700; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  ' Approve your Press Book entry

div style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 30px 0 30px 0;"
  => link_to "Log in here", dashboard_url
  ' to access the Winners' Dashboard to:
  br
  br
  ul
    li check the Press Book entry (a factual account of why you have won the Award and not a promotional press opportunity)
    li check the other details for your organisation are correct
    li provide details of a contact for press enquiries
  br
  ' Then click the "Submit" button by
  span style="font-weight: 700;"
    = @book_notes_deadline
  ' . If you do not respond by the deadline we will use the proposed text together with the contact details that we already hold.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  ' A link to the Winners' Resources to gain access to The Queen's Awards emblems and Winners' Manual is also on your online account.
  br
  | By accepting the Award, you agree to the terms and conditions set out in the Winners' Manual.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;"
  ' An invitation to HM The Queen's Reception at Buckingham Palace on
  => @attendees_invite_date
  ' will be sent in due course.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 38px 0 38px 0;"
  ' Congratulations once again on your Award.

p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 38px 0 38px 0;"
  ' Yours sincerely
  br
  br
  ' Nichola Bruno
  br
  ' The Secretary, The Queen's Awards for Enterprise
